      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll try the food thing. i was also reading online about lithium toxicity though and it said nausea and tremors are actually warning signs... do you think that could be what's happening to me or is that just being dramatic online? i feel like if i go to the doctor every time i feel a bit shaky it's a waste of their time.",
